      "id": "884178801456596",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "A masterclass in low-poly aesthetic!",
      "review_description": "​I’m absolutely obsessed with the low-poly art style of this game. The color palette is top-notch, and the scenes are so creative and interesting to look at—it’s visually refreshing and never feels overwhelming.\n​The variety of props is much deeper than I expected. Every new area is packed with interactive items and hidden details that keep the gameplay fresh. The devs really nailed the balance between a minimalist look and high-quality scene design. It’s so immersive that I found myself losing track of time just exploring the world. A total hidden gem! ✨💎",
      "date": 1769421990,
      "review_helpful_count": 8,
      "author_display_name": "joccob",
      "author_alias": "joccob",
      "developer_response": null
    },
