      "id": "867876116095305",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Overall, Blaster Bots is a great game",
      "review_description": "The controls are smooth, the movement and physics are well-done, and the combat is very satisfying. The unique feature of using one hand for weapons and the other for picking up items and attacking is quite interesting and keeps the gameplay from feeling repetitive.\n\nThe graphics are in a low-poly style, but they look very pleasing, and the color scheme is nice. There are many interactive elements in the environments, and sometimes you can spend a long time just running around the map and trying out different items.",
      "date": 1769502546,
      "review_helpful_count": 5,
      "author_display_name": "wenmangzhun",
      "author_alias": "wenmangzhun",
      "developer_response": null
