      "id": "1021935660997382",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Surprisingly relaxing for a shooter",
      "review_description": "ometimes you don't want a sweaty competitive match; you just want to blast some mobs and chill. This game is perfect for that. The low-poly art style is cute and clean, and the open maps let you roam freely. I love hoarding all the different items and just messing around with the physics. Pure, unadulterated fun.",
